[SN]TITLE[SN]
Threats made following roadside argument on the A483

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A motorcyclist has been threatened during a roadside argument with a man who is believed to have had a weapon, Dyfed-Powys Police said.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The incident happened on the A483, which runs through Carmarthenshire and Powys, near Llanwrtyd Wells.
Police said the biker was left shaken following the confrontation.
The incident happened at 20:00 BST on Friday and police appealed for witnesses to call 101.
